https://leetcode.com/problems/palindrome-partitioning/description/

QUESTION:
Input: s = "aab"
Output: [["a","a","b"],["aa","b"]]
SOLUTION:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
TIME  COMPLEXITY:O(2*2^n)
SPACE COMPLEXITY:O(n)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Start with empty:
[]

Pick from index 0:

Pick "a" (0→0 is palindrome):
[a]

From index 1:
Pick "a" (1→1 is palindrome):
[a, a]

From index 2:
Pick "b" (2→2 is palindrome):
[a, a, b] ✅ (add to result)

→ No more elements → backtrack

Backtrack:
[a, a, b] → [a, a]

From [a, a]:
→ No more choices → backtrack

Backtrack:
[a, a] → [a]

From [a]:
Try "ab" (1→2) ❌ not palindrome

→ No more choices → backtrack

Backtrack:
[a] → []

Pick "aa" (0→1 is palindrome):
[aa]

From index 2:
Pick "b" (2→2 is palindrome):
[aa, b] ✅ (add to result)

→ No more elements → backtrack

Backtrack:
[aa, b] → [aa] → []

Pick "aab" (0→2) ❌ not palindrome

Final Result:
[["a","a","b"], ["aa","b"]]
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CODE:
class Solution {
    List<List<String>>result=new ArrayList<>();
    public List<List<String>> partition(String s) {
        backtrack(s,0,new ArrayList<>());
        return result;
    }
    public void backtrack(String s,int index,ArrayList<String>temp){
        if(index==s.length()){
            result.add(new ArrayList<>(temp));
            return;
        }
        for(int i=index;i<s.length();i++){
            if(isPalindrome(s,index,i)){
                temp.add(s.substring(index,i+1));
                backtrack(s,i+1,temp);
                temp.remove(temp.size()-1);
            }
        }
    }
     public boolean isPalindrome(String s,int l,int r){
        while(l<r){
            if(s.charAt(l)!=s.charAt(r))return false;
            l++;
            r--;
        }
        return true;
    }
}
